
Percona
A puppet module for managing the installation of percona and restoring a mysql percona backup.

Implemented Features:

Installs percona and restores mysql percona backup on machine
Dependencies

Mysql and mysql percona backup

To include this module in nodes.pp on mysql node follow the following example
# MySQL Nodes
node "mysql.vagrant.com" 
    {
        include percona 
    }

Please donot run this module in production environment as because it
cleans mysql data directory before restoring from the backup

















